{
  "chapter": 114,
  "chapter_summary": "燕南天押着江别鹤来到小镇，赌场里的轩辕三光、屠娇娇、白开心三人目睹了燕南天的威风。小仙女张菁和顾人玉也来到小镇，小仙女挑衅江别鹤，却被燕南天轻松制服。燕南天揭露江别鹤的真面目，命他永不能欺世盗名。江玉郎出现，假称认识小鱼儿，将燕南天骗走。屠娇娇推断江别鹤就是江琴，燕南天正带他寻找小鱼儿。十大恶人趁机商议要为花无缺和铁心兰举办婚礼。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "格老子，真他妈的是天光、人光、钱光，反正弄不到鸟蛋精光，老子也睡不着觉。",
      "tone": "粗犷豪放",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们两个龟儿子为什么还不走，难道还想跟老子赌？",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这里只有一个半龟儿子，还有半个是龟女儿。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这里只有一个龟儿子，我却是你祖奶奶。",
      "tone": "嬉笑",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你放心，那赌鬼的轻功一向并不高明，咱们一定能追得上。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你这是干什么？难道撞见了鬼么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是撞见了大头鬼。",
      "tone": "惊恐",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子长得倒真有些奇怪，江湖中有这么样一个怪人，我居然没听说过，也没有见过，可见我这些年来实在太懒了。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "恶赌鬼，你认得这人么？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不认得。",
      "tone": "简洁",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江别鹤怎会没有跟着魏无牙？反而跟这怪人走到一起来了？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，快来呀，你骑的马难道是三条腿的么？",
      "tone": "娇嗔",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "不是我慢，而是你骑得实在太快了。",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "谁敢说我马骑得太快，我撞过人么？",
      "tone": "刁蛮",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "这样才乖，姐姐请你吃宵夜。",
      "tone": "俏皮",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天真可说是九丫头的好日子，我也很开心，所以我一定要大吃一顿，而且还要喝两杯。",
      "tone": "开心",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "你叹什么气？九丫头心上有了别的人，你难道很难受么？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "我怎会难受，我……我……",
      "tone": "结巴",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不难受最好，你看，这里居然还有粉蒸肉，还有珍珠丸子，我已经有好几年没有吃过这种小吃了，因为除了湖北外，别的地方做的都不好吃。",
      "tone": "兴奋",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "你看，那是什么人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他怎会到了这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "是呀，堂堂的江南大侠，怎会躲到这种小地方来了，难道是已经不敢见人了么，难怪江湖中人都说江大侠已失踪了。",
      "tone": "讽刺",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "江别鹤，江大侠，你为什么不开口了？你以前不是能说会道的吗？而且我还记得你的威风不小。",
      "tone": "讽刺",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "江别鹤，你用不着装傻，装傻也没用，不知有多少人正等着找你算一算旧账，你就跟着我走吧。",
      "tone": "严厉",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "他不能跟你走！",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "他为什么不能跟你走？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "只因他要跟我走。",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "跟你走，你是什么东西！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是谁家的子弟？怎的不分皂白，就敢对人下这么重的手？江湖中的后辈，怎地越来越不懂规矩了？",
      "tone": "严厉",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "你才是后辈小子！你才不懂规矩，你可知道……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "我被人如此欺负，你非但不帮我的忙，还不准我说话，你还能算是男人么？难怪别人要叫你顾小妹了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……我实在……",
      "tone": "结巴",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "阁下武功的确高明，但在下还是要来领教领教。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "留神，我要出手了！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "你是顾老四的什么人？",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "前……前辈莫非认得家父？",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "听说顾老四的家教很严，怎容得你这样的子弟在江湖中招摇？要知越是会武功的人，越该要自己收敛，若是一言不合就胡乱出手，那就是盗贼匹夫所为，这道理你爹爹难道未曾教训过你么？",
      "tone": "训斥",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "你究竟是什么人？凭什么来教训我们？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们连他老人家是谁都不知道么？他就是大侠燕南天！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江别鹤以后永远再也不能欺世盗名，为非作歹了，你们也用不着再找他算账，因为已有别的人要先找他算账，那是二十年前的旧账。",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "是，是……",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只望你们以后也莫要以武凌人，妄动杀手！",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们走吧。",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "你龟儿子现在为什么不叫了？听说你们将燕南天在恶人谷中困了二十年，老子本来还不相信，现在看来，只怕真有这回事。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是她和大嘴狼他们干的事，与我无关。",
      "tone": "推脱",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "既然与你无关，你龟儿子为什么怕成这副样子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你见了他难道不害怕么？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "老子坏事做得没有你多，用不着像你龟儿子这么害怕。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "常言道，只有强奸的，没有逼赌的，可见逼人赌钱要比强奸更坏，我干的坏事最多也只不过是强奸而已，可是你……嘿嘿，你小子等着瞧吧，他若知道你就是恶赌鬼，不打扁你的脑袋才怪。",
      "tone": "挑拨",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江别鹤这龟儿子怎会和燕南天走到一路的？这倒真是怪事。",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我现在才想出江别鹤的来历了。",
      "tone": "恍然大悟",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "他有什么来历？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他一定就是江琴。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "江琴又是什么人？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕南天到恶人谷去，就是为了要找江琴复仇，因为江琴害了他的拜把兄弟江枫。",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "他既要找江琴复仇的，现在为何还不宰了他，反而带着他满街跑呢？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他要先找到小鱼儿，叫小鱼儿亲手报仇。",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，想必就是这缘故，可是，他若找不到小鱼儿呢？",
      "tone": "担忧",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他这辈子只怕是再也找不到那小坏蛋了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这龟儿岂非就是江别鹤的儿子江玉郎么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一点也不错。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这父子两人究竟在搞什么鬼？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来他必定是想来救他老子的。",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就凭这小杂种，只怕还没有这么大的本事。",
      "tone": "不屑",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他本事虽不大，花样却不少，连小鱼儿有时都会上他的当。",
      "tone": "评价",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老子也知道他花样不少，但若要比小鱼儿，他还差得远。",
      "tone": "不屑",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你真的认得江小鱼？",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "非但认得，而且还可以说是患难之交。",
      "tone": "赔笑",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你……你最近见过他么？",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "前两天他还和晚辈在一起喝酒……",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你可知道他现在到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "他的行踪一向很飘忽，但晚辈却也许能找得到他。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "晚辈就算有天大的胆子，也不敢在前辈面前说谎。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，好，好……",
      "tone": "欢喜",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "这小子来历不明，燕大侠你怎可轻信他说的话？",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "闭嘴，在我面前，那有你说话之处？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 114
    }
